                                                                   GREP                  AND        SED
                                                      GLOBAL REGULAR EXPRESSION PRINT           STREAM EDITOR

                                                                                GREP
1/:grep class file1 >| to find word outside VIM

2/:grep cLAss file1 -i >| if you use capital alphabet like A M K D V this so no matter if you use this -i

3/:grep 'all\|linux' file1 >| to find multiple words

4/:grep 'good\|today\|class' file1 >|to find 3 words 

         A                               B
5/:grep hai file1 -i     :cat file1 then enter grep hai -i
both are same to find words

